{"tid":179748,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國股票，你問我答","createTime":"2017-03-30T12:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T07:14:42.000Z","uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd9ac813ee39f1000a9feb35fbae9b452ff526f3","tid":179748,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T12:36:58.000Z","msg":"強勢股就好似大波妹／巨乳美女，好獨凸！離遠都可以睇到<br />\n<br />\n強勢股可以用好多唔同既策略搵出來！<br />\n但係講點樣搵出來之前，首先要問點解要買強勢股？<br />\n好撚簡單，你想唔想同大波妹做愛？同大波妹做愛，可以令你好開心！<br />\n同樣買到強勢股，享受強勁既升浪，賺錢都可以好撚開心！<br />\n<br />\n係美國市場，強勢股（即係買入股價動力較強既股票策略係大幅outperform標普）<br />\nMTUM係追動力既指數基金，係近3年既表現都係大幅outperform標普！所以可想而知，買美股就係要追動力<br />\n<br />\n點樣可以搵到強勢股？<br />\n有好多書都有講 例如：William O Neil CANSLIM model<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51nqaD0D2%2BL._SX329_BO1,204,203,200_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F51nqaD0D2%252BL._SX329_BO1%2C204%2C203%2C200_.jpg&h=71985a48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又例如:inter market analysis 作者：John J Murphy <br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51Q%2Bxts%2Bd7L._AC_UL320_SR222,320_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F51Q%252Bxts%252Bd7L._AC_UL320_SR222%2C320_.jpg&h=de5bd0ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又例如：多空操作書 既作者：Stan Weinstein<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51RXsBGJhxL._SY344_BO1,204,203,200_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F51RXsBGJhxL._SY344_BO1%2C204%2C203%2C200_.jpg&h=61eed219&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDual momentum strategy<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/511HIhf-VpL._SX329_BO1,204,203,200_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F511HIhf-VpL._SX329_BO1%2C204%2C203%2C200_.jpg&h=016ca865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.superbookcity.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/image/450x/715771d2ae63ec7b2fe0bfb0e579e730/1/3/13495124_491322657742764_871705411691804304_n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.superbookcity.com%2Fmedia%2Fcatalog%2Fproduct%2Fcache%2F1%2Fimage%2F450x%2F715771d2ae63ec7b2fe0bfb0e579e730%2F1%2F3%2F13495124_491322657742764_871705411691804304_n.png&h=aca97b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nbtw,美股隊長串柒柒，但本書的確寫得好好！可以先睇美股隊長本書，之後再去睇番上面既書來學習<br />\n<br />\n所有美國既交易員同技術分析師都指出買強勢股係好既策略<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講咁撚多都沒用，巴打如果有咩股票想問，我會用上面個幾本書所學到既皮毛野來幫大家決定，巴打問既股票係唔係強勢股！？<br />\n<br />\n至於點解我咁撚得閒開post,屌你廢青，梗係得閒!<br />\n我唔係證監持牌既人士，所以我唔能夠俾咩意見，不過同天晴巴打一樣想同大家一齊討論強勢股！<br />\n<br />\n即管問！<br />\n<br />\n但係問之前，想分享一個大市策略！<br />\n就係當指數收市價跌穿200天線，就要全面對沖／沽出投資組合中所有持股！<br />\n因為當指數大力穿200天線，已經係反映跌浪既開始！Smart Money係200天之被突破之前，已經走貨！<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ.1美股邊到開户口？<br />\n富x牛x,Interacxxxx Brxxxxx,TD amertixxxxx, Charlxx Sxxxxx<br />\n<br />\nQ.2美股幾時見頂？<br />\n唔撚知<br />\n<br />\nQ.3點樣搵出美國既增長股？<br />\n<a href=\"http://stockcharts.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstockcharts.com&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=ca6ecd6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">stockcharts.com</a><br />\ninvestors business dairy<br />\nmarket watch<br />\nseeking alpha<br />\n頭兩個都係收費既服務<br />\n<br />\nQ.4美股係唔係同香港一樣一手手買賣架？<br />\n唔係，美股係一手一手，所以即使你户口好少錢，都可以買賣到股票！一千美元既户口都可以買到美股<br />\n<br />\nQ.5如果想炒衍生工具-期權應該睇咩書?<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.cp1897.com.hk/bookinfo/image/450/9789881944955z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cp1897.com.hk%2Fbookinfo%2Fimage%2F450%2F9789881944955z.jpg&h=8fd1a9a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基本入門<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.winmoney.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/%E6%9C%9F%E6%AC%8A2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.winmoney.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2F%25E6%259C%259F%25E6%25AC%258A2.jpg&h=c95474af&s={SIZE}\" /